Raspberry Pi5 cooling fan control driver

Syntax
%C [options]

Options:
    -v      Verbose level

Examples:
    # To read fan speed, range: 0 ~ 255
    cat /dev/fan

    # To turn off fan, write 0 to /dev/fan
    echo 0 > /dev/fan

    # To turn on fan or adjust fan speed, write value between 1 ~ 255 to /dev/fan
    # Please be aware that using value too small, PWM may not have enough
    # power to drive the fan

    echo 130 > /dev/fan
